2 1/4.
   Sumitomo Heavy Industries Ltd. (Japan) -- $340 million of
Eurobonds due Oct. 4, 1994, with equity-purchase warrants,
indicating a 5 1/8% coupon at par, via Daiwa Europe Ltd.
Guaranteed by Sumitomo Bank. Each $5,000 bond carries one
